docs/master-plan-20260409.md:3:Four systems need work in the right order: **CypherClaw** (art organism), **PromptClaw** (toolkit/dev), **sdp-cli** (core pipeline), **R750** (work deployment). This document sequences all of them to avoid thrashing, blocked dependencies, or duplicated effort.
docs/master-plan-20260409.md:11:| **sdp-cli** | Core pipeline infrastructure | 1 bug fixed (98da2b4), 4 more identified | Separate sdp-cli agent |
docs/master-plan-20260409.md:17:2. **Fix infrastructure bugs before features.** sdp-cli retry cascade costs 15-20% throughput on every project.
docs/master-plan-20260409.md:30:| Restart CypherClaw SDP runner with sdp-cli fix | CypherClaw | ✅ Done | — |
docs/master-plan-20260409.md:33:| Deliver sdp-cli bug report | sdp-cli agent | ✅ Done (this session) | — |
docs/master-plan-20260409.md:51:2. **Monitor from a distance.** Check `sdp-cli tasks list` every few hours. Don't restart, don't reload, don't load new PRDs.
docs/master-plan-20260409.md:52:3. **If it stalls again:** Pull sdp-cli updates, reset breaker, resume. The fix is in.
