+10   distrokid_isrc   TEXT     0                           0
+11   created_at       TEXT     1        CURRENT_TIMESTAMP  0
+12   updated_at       TEXT     1        CURRENT_TIMESTAMP  0
+```
 
+Durable Object storage also remained metadata-only for the T-054 route:
